  "time_ut": 1658565471,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel for school buses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe ordered the Minister of Transport to provide fuel for buses and vans transporting school children from today at all Langama depots across the island.",
        "The President gave these instructions during the discussion held this morning (23) on the fuel problem and its next steps.",
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe also advised the concerned parties to speed up and regularize the fuel distribution throughout the island.",
        "There was a wide discussion on regular and expedited fuel distribution for private and government buses engaged in education, fishing, tourism, agriculture and public transport.",
        "Education Minister Mr. Susil Premajayant drew the President's attention to the provision of necessary transportation facilities for school children when starting schools across the island from next Monday.",
        "It was also decided to release fuel for agricultural activities including fishing, tourism and fertilizer distribution, as well as for public transport activities through Langama depots and at tri-army camps across the island.",
        "Attention was also drawn to the smuggling of fuel obtained from fuel queues for selling vehicles at higher prices and the President instructed the police to expand related raids and strictly enforce the law against related individuals and groups.",
        "The quick implementation of the introduced QR code system was also discussed. A discussion was also held between the President and the officials of the Ministry of Finance and the State Bank regarding the upcoming fuel purchase activities and the provision of the required funds."
      ],
